WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 6=

00:00:43.790 --> 00:00:45.070
My child...

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:48.880
Who did this?

00:00:52.670 --> 00:00:53.510
Dear.

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:54.480
Dear.

00:01:23.180 --> 00:01:24.780
(Jiang Mansion)

00:01:24.790 --> 00:01:25.630
Mr. Jiang,

00:01:26.920 --> 00:01:28.150
my child

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:32.480
was lost yesterday

00:01:33.070 --> 00:01:34.040
at your place.

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:37.200
Mr. Huo, please calm down.

00:01:37.400 --> 00:01:38.240
This...

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:39.950
This was purely an accident.

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:41.766
My daughter was ignorant.

00:01:41.950 --> 00:01:43.430
She put something unpleasant

00:01:43.430 --> 00:01:44.950
into the cakes.

00:01:45.710 --> 00:01:46.550
Originally,

00:01:46.950 --> 00:01:49.070
she only meant to play a prank on Ruoli.

00:01:49.430 --> 00:01:50.270
Unexpectedly,

00:01:50.680 --> 00:01:51.640
it caused a miscarriage.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:52.840
Mr. Huo,

00:01:53.070 --> 00:01:54.840
this is a huge misunderstanding.

00:01:55.430 --> 00:01:56.270
A misunderstanding?

00:02:01.070 --> 00:02:01.910
Jiang Wanyue,

00:02:03.120 --> 00:02:05.560
I've had your cakes examined.

00:02:06.230 --> 00:02:07.536
They contained abortion medicine.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.766
Is that a misunderstanding?

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:11.400
Father, save me.

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:12.240
I know I was wrong.

00:02:12.240 --> 00:02:13.133
I'll never dare again.

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:14.280
Never again.

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:15.446
- Mr. Huo.
- Please spare me.

00:02:15.470 --> 00:02:16.400
Please spare her.

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:17.920
She may have done wrong,

00:02:18.173 --> 00:02:19.353
but she doesn't deserve death.

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:22.030
Do you intend to start a massacre

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:23.470
in my house?

00:02:25.630 --> 00:02:26.470
Shitou.

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:30.560
Yes.

00:02:30.590 --> 00:02:32.120
Take Jiang Wanyue back with us.

00:02:32.470 --> 00:02:33.756
I'll interrogate her personally.

00:02:33.910 --> 00:02:35.030
- Yes.
- Mr. Huo.

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:36.200
Mr. Huo.

00:02:36.560 --> 00:02:38.280
- Father, save me.
- Wanyue.

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.710
Guards, take her away.

00:02:40.630 --> 00:02:41.470
Father!

00:02:41.630 --> 00:02:42.470
Father!

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:43.920
Father!

00:02:44.590 --> 00:02:45.840
Father, save me!

00:02:50.750 --> 00:02:51.630
Let go of me.

00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:54.280
Jiang Ruoli, you wretch.

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:55.120
Let go of me.

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.470
How dare you call me a wretch?

00:02:59.030 --> 00:03:00.590
If we speak of that word,

00:03:00.590 --> 00:03:02.030
even if I studied for ten more years,

00:03:02.030 --> 00:03:03.280
I could never compare to you.

00:03:04.470 --> 00:03:06.080
We share the same Jiang blood

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.080
and are both women.

00:03:08.240 --> 00:03:09.360
Yet to frame me,

00:03:09.710 --> 00:03:11.430
you brought that thug Zhang San

00:03:11.430 --> 00:03:12.280
to ruin my virginity.

00:03:13.910 --> 00:03:15.310
You're so cruel.

00:03:15.750 --> 00:03:17.280
Even if I had some disgrace,

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:19.710
I'm far better than you.

00:03:21.030 --> 00:03:21.910
Virginity?

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:23.870
Even if Zhang San failed,

00:03:23.870 --> 00:03:25.120
you are still a loose woman.

00:03:25.859 --> 00:03:27.235
You and Huo Linchuan

00:03:27.246 --> 00:03:28.560
were sleeping together in secret.

00:03:28.560 --> 00:03:29.853
You're pregnant before marriage,

00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.393
yet pretending to be innocent here.

00:03:32.800 --> 00:03:33.640
My body

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:34.960
and my heart

00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:36.280
have always been mine to decide.

00:03:37.570 --> 00:03:38.609
If the rules of this world

00:03:38.620 --> 00:03:40.233
can't tolerate true love,

00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:41.800
they are not good rules.

00:03:42.680 --> 00:03:44.910
Instead of watching
whether I follow propriety,

00:03:45.080 --> 00:03:46.120
you should think carefully

00:03:46.910 --> 00:03:48.310
why a woman's life

00:03:48.310 --> 00:03:49.520
must be judged by others.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.190
You are rebellious,

00:03:51.710 --> 00:03:53.520
just like a shameless prostitute.

00:03:55.310 --> 00:03:56.910
Perhaps you should think carefully.

00:03:57.630 --> 00:03:58.816
From the moment you were born,

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:01.360
Uncle treated you
as a tool to ingratiate

00:04:01.360 --> 00:04:02.630
and trade for his career.

00:04:03.910 --> 00:04:05.900
How are you any different
from livestock or goods

00:04:05.911 --> 00:04:07.133
displayed for others to choose?

00:04:07.270 --> 00:04:08.110
You...

00:04:08.120 --> 00:04:08.960
Tell me.

00:04:10.096 --> 00:04:11.549
On the night of the Lantern Festival,

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:13.560
where did you go with Uncle?

00:04:15.030 --> 00:04:15.870
That night,

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:18.510
I was watching lanterns
with you and the family.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.390
Have you forgotten?

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:24.310
After the men in black
attacked our carriage,

00:04:25.190 --> 00:04:26.360
where did you go?

00:04:37.430 --> 00:04:38.550
Jiang Ruoli,

00:04:38.550 --> 00:04:39.430
what are you doing?

00:04:39.430 --> 00:04:40.270
Are you crazy?

00:04:43.270 --> 00:04:44.830
I know you've loved beauty

00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:45.950
since childhood.

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:50.000
I wonder

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:51.420
if this branding iron...

00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:52.390
What are you doing?

00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:54.430
If it were to land on your face,

00:04:54.920 --> 00:04:58.210
would you become
the most beautiful lady in the capital?

00:04:59.310 --> 00:05:00.160
That...

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:01.653
That night, after the crowd scattered,

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.040
Father left.

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:05.240
He left me alone to watch the lanterns.

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:07.560
Where did he go?

00:05:07.830 --> 00:05:08.920
I truly don't know.

00:05:10.190 --> 00:05:11.800
He just warned

00:05:12.190 --> 00:05:14.750
that I could return home
only after the Zi hour.

00:05:16.630 --> 00:05:17.470
(The Zi hour.)

00:05:20.460 --> 00:05:21.310
Is that true?

00:05:21.430 --> 00:05:22.390
Absolutely true.

00:05:22.860 --> 00:05:23.720
Ruoli,

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:25.070
please let me go.

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:35.000
Milady.

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:36.880
Milady.

00:05:39.310 --> 00:05:40.310
Jiang Ruoli.

00:05:41.310 --> 00:05:42.150
Wanyue.

00:05:42.480 --> 00:05:44.830
- Master.
- Father, look at my hands.

00:05:45.360 --> 00:05:46.510
So serious.

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:49.510
Jiang Ruoli.

00:05:50.070 --> 00:05:51.190
Huo Linchuan.

00:05:51.560 --> 00:05:53.000
If I don't avenge this,

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.190
how can I face everyone?

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:13.560
Dear,

00:06:14.480 --> 00:06:15.480
you just miscarried.

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:17.253
Your blood and energy are both depleted.

00:06:17.630 --> 00:06:19.430
Why didn't you drink the tonic?

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:22.880
Mr. Huo,

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:24.360
is the act over now?

00:06:24.750 --> 00:06:26.160
There was never anything there.

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:27.160
What is there to nourish?

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:31.240
That is not for you to decide.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:42.160
You did it on purpose.

00:06:43.236 --> 00:06:44.362
If we are putting on a show,

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:45.920
we must go all the way.

00:06:46.830 --> 00:06:48.310
Everyone in the mansion

00:06:48.310 --> 00:06:49.800
knows you miscarried.

00:06:50.870 --> 00:06:52.720
For me to feed you personally

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:54.680
is only proper.

00:06:59.510 --> 00:07:00.350
Oh.

00:07:02.070 --> 00:07:03.600
Or perhaps you

00:07:04.322 --> 00:07:05.608
prefer another method of feeding?

00:07:30.270 --> 00:07:32.000
Like this?

00:08:14.720 --> 00:08:15.800
Suddenly, I remember

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:17.480
something very important to do.

00:08:17.666 --> 00:08:18.679
I'll take my leave first.

00:08:31.240 --> 00:08:32.080
Milady,

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:33.373
is the water temperature okay?

00:08:33.750 --> 00:08:34.590
Yes.

00:08:55.630 --> 00:08:56.470
(Milady,)

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:58.440
(I have no choice.)

00:09:03.030 --> 00:09:03.870
Ruyan.

00:09:05.840 --> 00:09:06.720
Milady.

00:09:07.030 --> 00:09:08.360
So many things have happened

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:09.340
that I forgot to ask you.

00:09:10.240 --> 00:09:11.750
Who is

00:09:12.030 --> 00:09:13.000
your beloved?

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:15.800
Milady,

00:09:16.550 --> 00:09:19.030
he is a childhood acquaintance.

00:09:19.630 --> 00:09:21.960
He works as a kitchen helper
at Chunman Tavern.

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.750
A childhood acquaintance.

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:27.280
How nice.

00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:29.910
Before your pregnancy shows,

00:09:29.910 --> 00:09:31.550
I'll choose an auspicious day for you

00:09:32.440 --> 00:09:34.550
and marry you off in grand style.

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:36.480
If you don't mind,

00:09:36.480 --> 00:09:38.169
I'll add that pair
of white jade bracelets

00:09:38.180 --> 00:09:39.390
to your dowry.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:44.670
Milady,

00:09:46.270 --> 00:09:47.110
I can no longer serve

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:50.480
by your side.

00:09:53.550 --> 00:09:54.390
Ruyan,

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:56.000
though you're my maid,

00:09:56.440 --> 00:09:57.390
we are like sisters.

00:09:58.270 --> 00:10:00.320
Now that you've found a good man,

00:10:01.390 --> 00:10:02.910
I'm truly happy for you.

00:10:10.270 --> 00:10:11.110
Milady,

00:10:11.550 --> 00:10:13.000
the water has grown a little cold.

00:10:14.000 --> 00:10:16.270
I'll add more hot water.

00:10:16.270 --> 00:10:17.110
Sure.

00:10:21.150 --> 00:10:22.630
You've truly disappointed me.

00:10:24.150 --> 00:10:24.990
Master,

00:10:25.150 --> 00:10:26.630
I really can't do it.

00:10:26.840 --> 00:10:29.040
Mrs. Huo has treated me
with great kindness.

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:29.880
I can't.

00:10:29.880 --> 00:10:31.080
What kindness?

00:10:32.550 --> 00:10:33.390
Ruyan,

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:35.080
your life

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.870
and the child in your belly

00:10:36.870 --> 00:10:38.120
were both given by me.

00:10:38.520 --> 00:10:40.390
What does Jiang Ruoli count for?

00:10:41.790 --> 00:10:43.960
Does she still see me as her uncle?

00:10:44.670 --> 00:10:48.200
Today, she made me lose face
in the mansion.

00:10:48.510 --> 00:10:50.200
If I don't avenge this,

00:10:50.200 --> 00:10:51.670
how can I face everyone?

00:10:52.630 --> 00:10:55.440
Master, I beg you.

00:10:56.390 --> 00:10:59.840
Can you spare the child and me?

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:03.320
I'm willing to serve to repay you.

00:11:24.390 --> 00:11:25.720
(I wasn't having a dream.)

00:11:26.390 --> 00:11:27.790
(What is happening to me?)

00:12:50.100 --> 00:12:51.620
♪The dream shattered♪

00:12:51.980 --> 00:12:53.660
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:12:53.660 --> 00:12:55.300
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:12:56.180 --> 00:12:57.740
♪How vague♪

00:12:58.140 --> 00:12:59.660
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:12:59.660 --> 00:13:01.900
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:13:02.700 --> 00:13:05.300
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:13:05.780 --> 00:13:08.620
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:13:09.260 --> 00:13:14.020
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:13:14.620 --> 00:13:16.140
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:13:16.540 --> 00:13:20.100
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:13:20.820 --> 00:13:22.380
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:13:22.780 --> 00:13:26.500
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:13:27.220 --> 00:13:30.060
♪Life after life♪

00:13:30.540 --> 00:13:33.220
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:13:33.860 --> 00:13:37.940
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:13:38.020 --> 00:13:41.060
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:13:41.220 --> 00:13:42.620
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:13:42.620 --> 00:13:45.740
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:13:45.820 --> 00:13:47.260
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:13:47.380 --> 00:13:51.140
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:13:51.860 --> 00:13:54.660
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:13:54.940 --> 00:13:57.780
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:13:58.100 --> 00:14:02.500
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:14:02.740 --> 00:14:05.660
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:14:05.780 --> 00:14:10.220
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:14:10.420 --> 00:14:16.140
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:14:16.580 --> 00:14:19.300
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:14:19.540 --> 00:14:22.260
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:14:22.700 --> 00:14:28.700
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪